{"word":"G5271 - ὑποκρίνομαι - hypokrínomai - hoop-ok-rin'-om-ahee - Feign","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑποκρίνομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypokrínomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-ok-rin'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Feign</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - காண்பி, நடி"},{"paragraph":"1. to take up another's statements in reference to what one has decided for oneself"},{"paragraph":"2. to make answer (speak) on the stage, to personate anyone, play a part"},{"paragraph":"3. to simulate, feign, pretend"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G5259 - ὑπό - hypó - hoop-o'/5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G2919 - κρίνω - krínō - kree'-no/2919\">G2919</a>; to <i>decide</i> (<i>speak</i> or <i>act</i>) <i>under</i> a false part, that is, (figuratively) <i>dissemble</i> (<i>pretend</i>): - feign.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4942/4942\">G4942</a>, <a href=\"#/G505/505\">G505</a>, <a href=\"#/G5271/5271\">G5271</a>, <a href=\"#/G5272/5272\">G5272</a>, <a href=\"#/G5273/5273\">G5273</a>"}]}